data.description: Welcome home to this Salem City charmer.  Walk to nearby Main St , Salem City center, and Roanoke College. The current owners have made beautiful updates to the home, showcasing it's original character. Enter into your cozy sitting room with built in bookshelves and Fireplace. Modern lighting fixtures attract your eyes to the soaring ceilings. Make your way into the updated kitchen with new back splash and quartz counter tops.  Explore the home to find your perfect home office - there are many great options! Yard is already fenced in so bring your pooches!
